<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Harvest Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Harvest Hills was established back in 1990 and has been a major hotspot for homebuyers and real estate investors alike.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Represented by the Ward 3 Councilor in the Calgary City Council, the community in Harvest Hills is surrounded by the Beddington Trail to the South and the Deerfoot Trail to the east. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Home to one of the most challenging Nine-Hole golf courses in the whole of Alberta, the Harvest Hills Real Estate comprises a wide variety of housing options including apartment condos, villas, townhomes and single-family detached homes available at an average price of $420,000. </p>
